'''ᱚᱞᱞᱩ ᱚᱨᱡᱩᱱ''' (ᱡᱟᱱᱟᱢ ᱘ ᱚᱯᱨᱮᱞ ᱑᱙᱘᱒) ᱫᱚ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛᱤᱭᱟᱹ ᱟᱠᱴᱚᱨ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ | ᱡᱟᱦᱟᱸᱭ ᱫᱚ ᱯᱩᱭᱞᱩ ᱛᱮᱞᱩᱜᱩ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟᱹᱢᱤ ᱞᱮᱫᱼᱟ |<ref>{{Cite web |title=Forbes 2015 Celeb 100: Mahesh, Kamal, Rajini, Suriya, Rajamouli, Prabhas, Kajal, Shruti make it to list |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/forbes-2015-celeb-100-mahesh-kamal-rajini-suriya-rajamouli-prabhas-kajal-shruti-make-it-659012 |website=International Business Times, India Edition |accessdate=12 December 2015|date=11 December 2015 }}</ref> ''[[ᱵᱤᱡᱮᱛᱟ]]'' ᱨᱮ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱜᱤᱫᱽᱨᱟᱹ ᱟᱠᱴᱚᱨ ''[[ᱰᱟᱰᱰᱤ (᱒᱐᱐᱑ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ)|ᱰᱟᱰᱰᱭ]]'' ᱨᱮ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱰᱟᱱᱥᱚᱨ ᱞᱮᱠᱟᱭ ᱠᱟᱹᱢᱤ ᱫᱚᱥᱟᱨ ᱚᱞᱞᱩ ᱫᱚ ᱯᱩᱭᱞᱩ ''[[ᱜᱚᱝᱜᱳᱛᱨᱤ (ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ)|ᱜᱚᱝᱜᱳᱛᱤ]]'' ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟ,ᱢᱤ ᱞᱮᱫᱼᱟ |<ref name=":0">{{cite web |url=http://www.sify.com/movies/gangothri-review-telugu-pclu0rgjaifdj.html |title=Review : Gangothri |last=A. S. |first=Sashidhar |publisher=Sify |date=28 March 2003 |accessdate=14 March 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150314170654/http://www.sify.com/movies/gangothri-review-telugu-pclu0rgjaifdj.html |archivedate=14 March 2015}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite web |url=http://www.idlebrain.com/trade/records/gangotri100dayscenters.html |title=Gangotri 100 days centers |publisher=idlebrain.com |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924114948/http://www.idlebrain.com/trade/records/gangotri100dayscenters.html |archivedate=24 September 2015 }}</ref>

ᱚᱱᱟ ᱛᱟᱭᱚᱢ ᱚᱞᱞᱩ ᱫᱚ [[ᱥᱩᱠᱩᱢᱟᱨ (ᱰᱤᱨᱮᱠᱴᱚᱨ)|ᱥᱩᱠᱩᱢᱟᱨ]]ᱼᱟᱜ ᱯᱩᱭᱞᱩ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ''[[ᱟᱨᱭᱟ (᱒᱐᱐᱔ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ)|ᱟᱨᱭᱟ]]'' ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟᱹᱢᱤ ᱞᱮᱫᱼᱟ |<ref name=":2">{{cite web |url=http://www.indiaglitz.com/channels/telugu/review/7086.html |title=Arya – A cocktail of fun and more fun |publisher=IndiaGlitz |accessdate=10 May 2004}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{cite web |url=http://www.idlebrain.com/movie/archive/mr-arya.html |title=Movie review – Arya |publisher=idlebrain.com |accessdate=7 May 2004}}</ref> ''ᱟᱨᱭᱟ'' ᱨᱮ ᱟᱡᱟᱜ ᱨᱳᱞ ᱫᱚ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱫᱳᱞᱟᱹᱲ ᱠᱚᱝᱠᱟ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ, ᱚᱱᱟ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱱᱟᱯᱟᱭ ᱟᱠᱴᱤᱝ ᱠᱷᱟᱹᱛᱤᱨ [[ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱯᱷᱮᱭᱟᱨ ᱟᱣᱟᱨᱰ ᱯᱷᱚᱨ ᱵᱮᱥᱴ ᱟᱠᱴᱚᱨᱼᱛᱮᱞᱩᱜᱩ|ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱯᱷᱮᱭᱟᱨ ᱛᱮᱞᱩᱜᱩ ᱟᱠᱴᱚᱨ ᱟᱣᱟᱨᱰ]] ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱱ ᱮ ᱵᱟᱪᱷᱚᱱ ᱞᱮᱱᱟ ᱟᱨ [[ᱱᱤᱫᱷ᱾ ᱟᱣᱟᱨᱰ]] ᱥᱮᱨᱤᱢᱳᱱᱤ ᱨᱮ ᱡᱳᱨᱤ ᱟᱣᱟᱨᱰ ᱟᱨ [[ᱥᱤᱱᱮᱢᱟᱟ ᱟᱣᱟᱨᱰ]], ᱱᱟᱯᱟᱭ ᱡᱳᱨᱤ ᱟᱨ ᱱᱟᱯᱟᱭ ᱟᱠᱴᱤᱝ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱱ ᱧᱟᱢ ᱞᱮᱫᱼᱟ |<ref name=":4">{{cite news |url=http://www.thehindu.com/2005/10/10/stories/2005101017920100.htm |title='Anand' walks away with six Nandi awards |newspaper=The Hindu |date=10 October 2005 |accessdate=14 March 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150314170957/http://www.thehindu.com/2005/10/10/stories/2005101017920100.htm |archivedate=14 March 2015}}</ref> ᱟᱨᱭᱟ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱫᱚ ᱱᱟᱯᱟᱭ ᱵᱮᱯᱟᱨ ᱠᱚ ᱦᱩᱭ ᱮᱢᱟᱱ ᱞᱮᱱᱟ |<ref name="Arya">{{cite news |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Allu-Arjuns-favourite-film-is-Arya/articleshow/34885248.cms |title=Allu Arjun's favourite film is Arya |newspaper=The Times of India |date=9 May 2014 |accessdate=14 March 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150314170652/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Allu-Arjuns-favourite-film-is-Arya/articleshow/34885248.cms |archivedate=14 March 2015 |url-status=dead}}</ref>

ᱚᱱᱟ ᱫᱚᱥᱟᱨ [[ᱵᱷᱤᱹᱵᱷᱤᱹ ᱵᱤᱱᱟᱭᱚᱠ]]ᱼᱟᱜ ''[[ᱵᱚᱱᱱᱤ (᱒᱐᱐ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ)|ᱵᱚᱱᱱᱤ]]'' ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟᱹᱢᱤ ᱞᱮᱫᱼᱟ | ᱚᱱᱟ ᱨᱮ ᱟᱡᱟᱜ ᱵᱮᱵᱷᱟᱨ ᱟᱨ ᱮᱱᱮᱡ ᱠᱷᱟᱹᱛᱤᱨ ᱠᱚ ᱧᱩᱢ ᱥᱟᱨᱦᱟᱣ ᱞᱮᱫᱮᱭᱟ |<ref name=":5">{{cite web |url=http://www.idlebrain.com/movie/archive/mr-bunny.html |title=Movie review – Bunny |publisher=idlebrain.com |accessdate=6 April 2005}}</ref> ᱚᱱᱟ ᱛᱟᱭᱚᱢ ᱟᱡᱟᱜ ᱫᱚᱥᱟᱨ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱫᱚ [[ᱮᱹ ᱠᱚᱨᱩᱬᱟᱠᱚᱨᱚᱱ]]ᱼᱟᱜ ᱫᱤᱞᱟᱹᱲ ᱠᱟᱛᱷᱟ ᱯᱷᱤᱯᱢ  ''[[ᱦᱮᱯᱯᱤ (᱒᱐᱐᱖ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ)|ᱦᱮᱯᱯᱤ]]'' ᱠᱟᱱᱟ |<ref name=":6">{{cite web |url=http://www.indiaglitz.com/channels/telugu/review/7969.html |title=Happy – Study of love |publisher=IndiaGlitz |accessdate=28 January 2006}}</ref> ᱚᱱᱟ ᱯᱚᱨᱮ [[ᱯᱩᱨᱤ ᱡᱚᱜᱚᱱᱱᱟᱫᱷ]]ᱼᱟᱜ ᱟᱠᱥᱚᱱ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ''[[ᱫᱮᱥᱢᱩᱫᱩᱨᱩ]]'' ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟᱹᱢᱤ ᱞᱮᱫᱼᱟ |<ref name=":7">{{cite web |url=http://www.indiaglitz.com/channels/telugu/review/8584.html |title=Desamuduru – Allu Arjun is now a macho man |publisher=IndiaGlitz |accessdate=12 January 2007}}</ref>

